result.cypher_query:
MATCH (drug)-[r:HAS_SIDE_EFFECT]->(effect)
        WHERE effect.name = 'dry mouth'
        RETURN drug.name AS drug_name
        ORDER BY drug.name

MATCH (drug)-[r:HAS_SIDE_EFFECT]->(effect)
        WHERE effect.name = 'cardiac arrest'
        RETURN drug.name AS drug_name
        ORDER BY drug.name
